# Hosts/URLs that the lychee link checker cannot reliably verify from CI.
# Lines are regular expressions matched against each URL. Links here are
# excluded from the (already advisory) external link check to keep its report
# meaningful. Entries are reviewed periodically; see ROADMAP.md.

# Expired or misconfigured TLS certificates (sites work in a normal browser).
